Replay.IO

Class ReplayScanner

  • java.lang.Object
    • Replay.IO.ReplayScanner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public final class ReplayScanner
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    Scanner-like class which emits Java analogues to .osr data-types.

    Attempting to retrieve data on EOF is an error in all cases.

        public java.lang.String nextString()

        Reads a string from the underlying stream.
